<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>E-Tracking Service Renewal Reminder</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;
      color: #000; background-color: #fff; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container {
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; }
      .confirmation-box-warning { background-color: #fff2f0; border: 2px solid
      #d0142b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; text-align:
      center; } .greeting { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; } .content {
      line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; } .details-table { width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #000;
      margin: 20px 0; table-layout: fixed; } .details-table th {
      background-color: #00aa00; color: white; font-weight: bold; text-align:
      center; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #000; } .details-table td {
      padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #000; font-size: 10pt; word-wrap:
      break-word; } .details-table .label { width: 40%; font-weight: bold; }
      .details-table .value { text-align: center; width: 60%; } .vehicles-table
      { width: 100%; max-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px
      solid #000; margin: 20px 0; table-layout: auto; } .vehicles-table th {
      background-color: #00aa00; color: white; font-weight: bold; text-align:
      center; padding: 6px 4px; border: 1px solid #000; font-size: 9pt;
      word-wrap: break-word; } .vehicles-table td { padding: 4px 2px; border:
      1px solid #000; font-size: 8pt; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;
      overflow-wrap: break-word; } .amount-highlight { font-weight: bold; color:
      #d9534f; } .signature { margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #009900;
      padding-top: 15px; } .contact-info { font-size: 10px; color: #808080;
      margin-top: 20px; } .urgent { color: #d9534f; font-weight: bold; }
      .payment-image { max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: auto; max-height:
      400px; display: block; margin: 10px auto; } /* Mobile responsive styles */
      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) { .container { padding: 10px; }
      .details-table, .vehicles-table { font-size: 9pt; } .details-table td,
      .vehicles-table td { padding: 4px 2px; font-size: 8pt; } .details-table
      th, .vehicles-table th { padding: 4px 2px; font-size: 8pt; }
      .vehicles-table th { font-size: 7pt; } .vehicles-table td { font-size:
      7pt; } .payment-image { max-width: 95%; max-height: 300px; } } @media
      screen and (max-width: 480px) { .vehicles-table { font-size: 7pt; }
      .vehicles-table th, .vehicles-table td { padding: 2px 1px; font-size: 6pt;
      } .payment-image { max-width: 90%; max-height: 250px; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
	
	<!-- Greeting Section -->
      <div class="greeting">
        <strong>السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته</strong>
      </div>


      <!-- Welcome Box -->
      <div class="confirmation-box-warning">
        <h2 style="color: #d0142b; margin: 0;">⚠️ RENEWAL PENDING</h2>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">The annual renewal payment of your
          E-Tracking service is still pending!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">

        Dear customer, we hope you are fine and in good health. Your E-Tracking
        account will be expired on service tenure end-date as mentioned below
        and your annual service renewal charges are still pending. Please find
        your service details, package upgradation options and payment methods
        below. Kindly pay your pending dues and share the screenshot or slip of
        payment transfer before expiry date in order to continue your service.
        We will forward your payment slip to IT team for your E-Tracking account
        renewal. Thank you.
      </div>

      <!-- 1st Table: Account & Service Details (with customer details) -->
      <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2">Account & Service Details</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Name</td>
          <td class="value">{{{customerName}}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label">CNIC / NTN</td>
          <td class="value">{{cnic}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Authorized POC</td>
          <td class="value">{{{contactNumber}}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Reference Number</td>
          <td class="value">{{referenceNumber}}</td>
        </tr>
        <!-- <tr> -->
        <!-- <td class="label">Total Vehicles</td> -->
        <!-- <td class="value">{{totalVehicles}}</td> -->
        <!-- </tr> -->
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Total Devices</td>
          <td class="value">{{totalDevices}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Service Type</td>
          <td class="value">Annual Renewal Payment Pending</td>
        </tr>
        {{#if notes}}
          <tr>
            <td class="label">Additional Notes</td>
            <td class="value">{{{notes}}}</td>
          </tr>
        {{/if}}
      </table>


      <!-- 2nd Table: Vehicles (with tenure end date) -->
      {{#if vehicles}}
        <table class="vehicles-table">
          <tr>
            <th>Unit #</th>
            <th>Reg #</th>
            <th>Model</th>
            <th>Package</th>
            <th>Amount</th>
            <th>Expiry Date</th>
          </tr>
          {{#each vehicles}}
            <tr>
              <td>{{rank}}</td>
              <td>{{regNumber}}</td>
              <td>{{model}}</td>
              <td>{{package}}</td>
              <td class="amount-highlight">{{amount}}</td>
              <td>{{endDate}}</td>
            </tr>
          {{/each}}
          <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
            <td colspan="4" style="font-weight: bold; text-align: right;">TOTAL
              AMOUNT PAYABLE:</td>

            <td
              class="amount-highlight"
              style="font-weight: bold;"
            >{{totalAmount}}</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="content">
        <strong class="urgent">Service Expiry Date: {{expiryDate}}</strong>
      </div>



      <!-- Section - Payment Methods -->
      <div class="content">
        <hr style="border: 1px solid #009900; margin: 20px 0;" />
        <strong><u>PAYMENT METHODS:</u></strong><br />
        Dear customer, now you can easily pay your dues online through following
        methods:<br /><br />

        <strong>Method-1 Easy Paisa Transfer</strong><br />
        Title: E-Tracking Solutions<br />
        Pay by Till Number: 0212135<br />
        Pay by scanning QR code attached below or download here:
        <a
          href="https://etracking.pk/easypaisa"
          target="_blank"
        >https://etracking.pk/easypaisa</a><br />
        Clearance time: same day if paid before COB<br /><br />

        <strong>Method-2 Meezan Bank Limited</strong><br />
        Branch: Islampura, Lahore<br />
        Title CEO: Mian Nirwan Farooqi<br />
        Account #: 0237-0101292005<br />
        IBAN #: PK22MEZN0002370101292005<br />
        Clearance time: same day if paid before COB<br /><br />

      </div>

      <div class="content" style="text-align: center;">
        <img
          src="cid:payment-options"
          alt="Payment Options QR Code"
          class="payment-image"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <strong>Kindly share the screenshot of payment transferred here or on
          official WhatsApp, so we can forward to IT team for renewal of your
          E-Tracking account. Thank you.</strong><br /><br />
        <u><i>Note: Any payment on any other account or by any other method will
            not be acceptable.</i></u>
      </div>

      <br />
      <br />


      <!-- Signature -->
      <div class="content" style="text-align: center;">
        <img
          src="https://etracking.pk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ETS-revamped-Header-Logo-2018-Hi-tiny.png"
          alt="E-Tracking Logo"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="signature">
        <div>
          Regards,<br />
          <br />
          <strong>Support Team</strong><br />
          E-Tracking Solutions<br />
          <br />
          Email: support@etracking.pk<br />
          Website: https://etracking.pk<br />
          Helpline:
          <a href="tel:+923111277547" target="_blank">
            03-111-277-547</a><br />

          WhatsApp:
          <a href="https://wa.me/923111277547" target="_blank">
            03-111-277-547</a><br />

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Info -->
      <div class="contact-info">
        This is an automated renewal reminder sent by E-Tracking Solutions.
        Please contact our support team at support@etracking.pk if you have any
        questions about your account or payment options.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>